  "content": [
    {
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "chapterTitle": "壹 汉代政府组织",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "3300012390_31_1068-1093",
          "range": "1068-1093",
          "rangeStart": 1068,
          "rangeEnd": 1093,
          "markText": "而且中国的立国规模，并不是向外征服，而是向心凝结。",
          "colorStyle": 0,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1719163139,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-06-24 01:18:59",
          "chapterUid": 31,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1068&rangeEnd=1093",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1068&rangeEnd=1093"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "bookReviews": [],
  "hotBookmarks": [
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_26_851-948",
      "chapterUid": 26,
      "range": "851-948",
      "markText": "而且制度是死的，人事是活的，死的制度绝不能完全配合上活的人事。就历史经验论，任何一制度，绝不能有利而无弊。任何一制度，亦绝不能历久而不变。历史上一切以往制度俱如是，当前的现实制度，也何尝不如是。",
      "totalCount": 2124,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=26&rangeStart=851&rangeEnd=948",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=26&rangeStart=851&rangeEnd=948"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_31_1068-1093",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "1068-1093",
      "markText": "而且中国的立国规模，并不是向外征服，而是向心凝结。",
      "totalCount": 1911,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1068&rangeEnd=1093",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=1068&rangeEnd=1093"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_44_2235-2271",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "2235-2271",
      "markText": "其实革命的本质，应该是推翻制度来迁就现实的，绝非是推翻现实来迁就制度的。",
      "totalCount": 1836,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=2235&rangeEnd=2271",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=44&rangeStart=2235&rangeEnd=2271"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_85_5103-5116",
      "chapterUid": 85,
      "range": "5103-5116",
      "markText": "再看一道，总还不是要不得。",
      "totalCount": 1222,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=85&rangeStart=5103&rangeEnd=5116",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=85&rangeStart=5103&rangeEnd=5116"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_39_2627-2695",
      "chapterUid": 39,
      "range": "2627-2695",
      "markText": "因此皇帝好，事情也做得好。皇帝坏了，而政治上并不曾有管束皇帝的制度，这是东汉政治制度上的一个大问题。也是将来中国政治制度史上一个大问题。",
      "totalCount": 1212,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=39&rangeStart=2627&rangeEnd=2695",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=39&rangeStart=2627&rangeEnd=2695"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_33_2986-3077",
      "chapterUid": 33,
      "range": "2986-3077",
      "markText": "我们可说中国历史上此下的政府，既非贵族政府，也非军人政府，又非商人政府，而是一个“崇尚文治的政府”，即士人政府。只许这些人跑上政治舞台，政府即由他们组织，一切政权也都分配在他们手里。",
      "totalCount": 1190,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=33&rangeStart=2986&rangeEnd=3077",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=33&rangeStart=2986&rangeEnd=3077"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_35_3271-3340",
      "chapterUid": 35,
      "range": "3271-3340",
      "markText": "我们此刻要讨论历史制度，全该注意当时的历史传统与当时人的历史意见，作为主要之参考。不该把我们的时代意见来抹杀当时的历史意见，这才是正办呀！",
      "totalCount": 1050,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=35&rangeStart=3271&rangeEnd=3340",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=35&rangeStart=3271&rangeEnd=3340"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_62_9889-9957",
      "chapterUid": 62,
      "range": "9889-9957",
      "markText": "任何一省都如此。给你这一半，割去你那一半。好使全国各省，都成支离破碎。既不能统一反抗，而任何一区域也很难单独反抗。这是行省制的内在精神。",
      "totalCount": 1044,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=62&rangeStart=9889&rangeEnd=9957",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=62&rangeStart=9889&rangeEnd=9957"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_31_2492-2528",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "2492-2528",
      "markText": "可见汉代一切实际事权，照法理，该在相府，不在皇室，宰相才是政府的真领袖。",
      "totalCount": 1037,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=2492&rangeEnd=2528",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=2492&rangeEnd=2528"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_31_711-739",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "711-739",
      "markText": "第一是皇室与政府之职权划分，第二是中央与地方的职权划分。",
      "totalCount": 918,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=711&rangeEnd=739",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=711&rangeEnd=739"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_44_4230-4290",
      "chapterUid": 44,
      "range": "4230-4290",
      "markText": "若要解决中国社会之积弊，则当使知识分子不再集中到政治一途，便该奖励工商业，使聪明才智转趋此道。然结果又很易变成资本主义。",
      "totalCount": 880,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=44&rangeStart=4230&rangeEnd=4290",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=44&rangeStart=4230&rangeEnd=4290"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_28_2557-2638",
      "chapterUid": 28,
      "range": "2557-2638",
      "markText": "中国历史上考试与选举两项制度，其用意是在政府和社会间打通一条路，好让社会在某种条件某种方式下来掌握政治，预闻政治，和运用政治，这才是中国政治制度最根本问题之所在。",
      "totalCount": 860,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2557&rangeEnd=2638",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=28&rangeStart=2557&rangeEnd=2638"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_46_1826-1894",
      "chapterUid": 46,
      "range": "1826-1894",
      "markText": "即就账籍制度言，可见每一项制度之推行与继续，也必待有一种与之相当的道德意志与服务忠诚之贯注。否则徒法不能以自行，纵然法良意美，终是徒然。",
      "totalCount": 814,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=46&rangeStart=1826&rangeEnd=1894",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=46&rangeStart=1826&rangeEnd=1894"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_31_6221-6238",
      "chapterUid": 31,
      "range": "6221-6238",
      "markText": "中央特派专员到地方来调查的叫刺史。",
      "totalCount": 810,
      "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=3300012390&chapterUid=31&rangeStart=6221&rangeEnd=6238",
      "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/90932f60813ab6b57g010132?chapterUid=31&rangeStart=6221&rangeEnd=6238"
    },
    {
      "bookmarkId": "3300012390_33_1504-1589",
      "chapterUid": 33,
